# Auto detect text files and perform LF normalization
* text=auto

# Python files
*.py text diff=python

# Documentation
*.md text diff=markdown
*.txt text
*.rst text

# Configuration files
*.yaml text
*.yml text
*.json text
*.toml text
*.ini text
*.cfg text
*.conf text

# BPMN files
*.bpmn text

# Scripts
*.sh text eol=lf
*.bat text eol=crlf

# Graphics
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.svg text

# Archives
*.7z binary
*.bz2 binary
*.gz binary
*.rar binary
*.tar binary
*.zip binary

# Fonts
*.eot binary
*.otf binary
*.ttf binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary

# Audio/Video
*.mp3 binary
*.mp4 binary
*.avi binary
*.mov binary
*.wmv binary
*.flv binary
*.wav binary
*.flac binary
*.aac binary

# Database
*.db binary
*.sqlite binary
*.sqlite3 binary

# Logs
*.log text

# Temporary files
*.tmp binary
*.temp binary
*.bak binary
*.swp binary
*.swo binary

# IDE files
.vscode/* text
.idea/* text
*.sublime-project text
*.sublime-workspace text

# OS generated files
.DS_Store binary
Thumbs.db binary
ehthumbs.db binary
Desktop.ini binary
